    </div>





	<div class="boxed"  style="background-image: url('https://rotoruanz-img-cdn.azureedge.net/rotoruanz/rotoruanz/media/campaign/whakarewarewa-forest-loop_nov2021_credit-graeme-murray-11_resized_2.jpg')">

