</div>

<div class="card-info__details">

		<h4>Whakarewarewa Forest Mountain Biking</h4>
		<p>Whakarewarewa Forest, also known as the Redwoods, is a mecca for mountain bikers, with 200km of trails winding their way through native and exotic forest.</p>

</div>

	<div class="card-info__footer">

		<a href="https://www.rotoruanz.com/things-to-do/cycling-mountain-biking/whakarewarewa-forest-mountain-biking" class="btn btn__link">Learn more</a>

