</div>

<div class="card-info__details">

		<h4>Electric Bike Rotorua</h4>
		<p>Explore Rotorua and experience the thrill of an electric bike doing the work for you while you check out Rotorua – and help save the planet at the same time!</p>

</div>

	<div class="card-info__footer">

