<div class="card-info__details">

		<h4>Whakarewarewa Forest Walking Trails</h4>
		<p>The walking trails in Whakarewarewa Forest, or "the Redwoods", start at the Redwoods i-SITE Visitor Information Centre where you can pick up a map before exploring the forest.</p>

</div>

	<div class="card-info__footer">

